<@section "Best time to visit" "viajar">
<p>
Capurganá is located on the Caribbean Cost of Colombia, near the Panama’s frontier and the Sapzurro’s bay. Because of its geographic position, from December to February, it receives winds from the north that difficult some aquatic activities and the sea access to fishers and launches. For this reason, we advice you to don’t travel by launch in this period, as the big waves combined with the launch speed don’t provide the best conditions. Then, the period from April to November is the best time to come and find crystalline water, perfect to learn and practice diving. 
</p>
